1
00:01:05,910 --> 00:01:07,580
This case is very strange.

2
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,000
As long as it's night,

3
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,870
villagers passing by the mass grave

4
00:01:10,870 --> 00:01:12,330
disappear inexplicably,

5
00:01:12,750 --> 00:01:14,610
leaving not even a corpse behind.

6
00:02:48,450 --> 00:02:50,040
To think there's such a monster in the world.

7
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,000
Miss,

8
00:02:51,540 --> 00:02:52,579
what is this?

9
00:02:52,829 --> 00:02:54,829
I only know they are harmful things.

10
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:57,950
The villagers who disappeared these days are related to it.

11
00:02:57,950 --> 00:02:59,620
I didn't believe in ghosts and gods,

12
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:01,450
but seeing it with my own eyes today,

13
00:03:01,450 --> 00:03:02,750
it's really strange.

14
00:03:03,790 --> 00:03:05,330
Heaven and Earth breed all things.

15
00:03:05,330 --> 00:03:06,530
Thank you today, sir.

16
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,770
The case is my responsibility.

17
00:03:08,950 --> 00:03:10,750
I should be the one thanking you.

18
00:03:11,290 --> 00:03:13,450
Recently, strange things have been happening frequently in the city.

19
00:03:13,450 --> 00:03:15,180
Since you have such abilities,

20
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:18,420
why not handle the bizarre cases with me?

21
00:03:18,829 --> 00:03:20,760
That's exactly what I have in mind.

22
00:03:21,790 --> 00:03:23,540
Are you used to living in the mansion?

23
00:03:23,540 --> 00:03:25,200
It's good. It's very quiet.

24
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:26,040
Quiet?

25
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,250
Is it too deserted?

26
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,160
No, I feel safe.

27
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:34,160
If anyone neglects you,

28
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,090
just let me know.

29
00:03:37,579 --> 00:03:39,000
There's a case recently.

30
00:03:39,329 --> 00:03:41,500
The Liu family's daughter died on her wedding night,

31
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:42,290
and the happy event turned into a funeral.

32
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:45,620
The strange thing is that during the three days of the vigil,

33
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:49,579
a woman's crying could be heard every night at the vigil site.

34
00:03:49,579 --> 00:03:50,700
But during the day,

35
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:52,170
the sound disappears.

36
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:54,329
Master Liu sent someone to invite a Taoist priest.

37
00:03:54,329 --> 00:03:55,040
They burned talismans

38
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:57,160
and chanted scriptures, but the crying remained.

39
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:59,250
Yesterday, they asked someone to find me at my mansion.

40
00:03:59,250 --> 00:04:00,660
I wonder if it's convenient for you.

41
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:01,660
It's convenient.

42
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:03,440
I'm not afraid.

43
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,290
The general is here.

44
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:52,950
Don't be afraid.

45
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:55,330
I will clear your grievance for you.

46
00:05:01,290 --> 00:05:02,820
You write poetry very well.

47
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:03,660
Between the lines,

48
00:05:03,660 --> 00:05:05,660
it's full of strength of character.

49
00:05:08,540 --> 00:05:10,070
You can't touch the coffin.

50
00:05:10,250 --> 00:05:11,790
She is a demoness.

51
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:13,580
She attracted the evil spirits

52
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:16,000
that disturbed our Liu Mansion.

53
00:05:19,330 --> 00:05:20,330
Where are you from, demoness?

54
00:05:20,330 --> 00:05:21,950
How dare you disturb the Yin and Yang here,

55
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:24,210
and destroy my evil-suppressing array!

56
00:05:24,950 --> 00:05:26,950
Stop pretending to be an orthodox Taoist priest.

57
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:28,680
What evil-suppressing magic?

58
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,870
This soul-locking array is obviously

59
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:31,290
an evil magic used to trap wronged souls.

60
00:05:31,290 --> 00:05:33,580
It's extremely sinister.

61
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:34,830
Nonsense!

62
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:36,159
I have been cultivating for many years,

63
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,830
and all the talismans I use are authentic.

64
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:40,560
What do you know, you wet-behind-the-ears brat?

65
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:42,980
Then let me show you the truth of the matter.

66
00:05:51,659 --> 00:05:54,040
Miss Liu, this poem is wonderful.

67
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:57,840
What a line: 'The spring breeze doesn't understand the intention.'

68
00:05:59,250 --> 00:06:00,080
Round when drawn,

69
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,040
square when written,

70
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,870
short when cold,

71
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:02,700
long when hot.

72
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:03,580
Guess a word.

73
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,910
Clouds float like works of art,

74
00:06:20,910 --> 00:06:22,660
stars shoot with grief at heart.

75
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:25,320
Across the Milky Way the Cowherd meets the Maid.

76
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:30,480
If love between both sides can last for aye,

77
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:32,870
why need they stay together night and day?

78
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:39,620
Our master said,

79
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:41,450
5,000 taels of silver as a betrothal gift,

80
00:06:41,450 --> 00:06:43,330
plus two shops in the south of the city,

81
00:06:43,330 --> 00:06:44,540
and a hundred acres of fertile land.

82
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:46,580
Miss Liu will be an honored concubine once she enters our door.

83
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:48,659
She will never be mistreated.

84
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:51,250
Qingyuan is going there to enjoy a good life.

85
00:06:51,250 --> 00:06:53,500
Someone with Master Song's character and background

86
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:55,370
is hard to find.

87
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,330
Of all things to learn,

88
00:07:00,330 --> 00:07:01,830
you learn from your mother who died early.

89
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,830
You only know how to write these worthless things.

90
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:05,490
You might as well marry early.

91
00:07:12,330 --> 00:07:13,260
Don't be afraid.

92
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:17,010
I'll take you away.

93
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:19,830
Catch that wretched girl and bring her back to me.

94
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:20,700
She must marry,

95
00:07:20,700 --> 00:07:22,230
whether she wants to or not.

96
00:07:22,290 --> 00:07:24,700
Beat that man named Shen to death.

97
00:07:31,250 --> 00:07:32,159
Let me go.

98
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:33,659
Let me go.

99
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,659
I'll do whatever you say.

100
00:07:35,659 --> 00:07:36,330
Let him go,

101
00:07:36,330 --> 00:07:37,730
and I'll go back with you.

102
00:07:43,909 --> 00:07:46,040
A bride should be happy.

103
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:48,020
Pulling a long face is so unlucky.

104
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:30,580
This is the deposit.

105
00:08:30,790 --> 00:08:33,870
I want you to make sure this wretched girl is never reincarnated.

106
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:35,659
Leave this to me.

107
00:08:35,659 --> 00:08:37,159
Rest assured.

108
00:08:37,289 --> 00:08:38,789
Miss Qingyuan has great talent.

109
00:08:38,789 --> 00:08:40,500
She only wishes to spend her life with poetry

110
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:41,700
and her lover.

111
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:44,000
Her heart and soul are in these poems,

112
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,370
and her character is in these words.

113
00:08:45,370 --> 00:08:47,330
They deserve to be seen by more people.

114
00:08:47,330 --> 00:08:48,910
But for the sake of money,

115
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:50,370
you sold her to Master Song

116
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:51,500
and ruined her life.

117
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,660
This is all an illusion cast by this witch.

118
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:55,830
She deliberately forged these scenes to slander me.

119
00:08:55,830 --> 00:08:59,500
That's right, this witch uses evil illusions to confuse people's minds.

120
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,660
I can see through her tricks at a glance.

121
00:09:01,660 --> 00:09:03,080
She is turning black into white

122
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,810
and making false accusations.

123
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,490
As the general ordered,

124
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:13,790
I have searched Madam Liu's courtyard and private storehouse.

125
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:15,910
This is the account book of her bribing court officials.

126
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,040
And the correspondence with Master Song

127
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:19,250
plotting Miss Liu's marriage contract.

128
00:09:19,250 --> 00:09:21,500
Madam Liu murdered the legitimate daughter,

129
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:22,910
and bribed court officials.

130
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:23,790
The evidence for each and every crime

131
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,830
is conclusive.

132
00:09:24,950 --> 00:09:26,700
Do you plead guilty?

133
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:27,200
I...

134
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,260
I'm going to report to the officials.

135
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:36,370
It's a good chance to test the soul lamp's limits

136
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:37,970
and report back to my master.

137
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,700
None of you will leave here alive today.

138
00:11:37,290 --> 00:11:39,290
This line is truly a stroke of genius.

139
00:11:39,290 --> 00:11:41,450
To think it can create such an artistic conception.

140
00:11:41,450 --> 00:11:42,160
Miss Liu,

141
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:45,090
they have all received the punishment they deserve.

142
00:11:45,330 --> 00:11:46,530
May you rest in peace.

143
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:50,390
Thank you both for your help.

144
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:16,330
Sister,

145
00:12:16,330 --> 00:12:17,830
I finally found you.
